      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Elle appakfcha rihbeja\npreekſch teiw/ tew pretti eijoht/\nład tu atnahzi/ winna uſmoh-\ndinaja tewis deht tohs Mirru-\nſchus/ wiſſus Leel-Kungus tahs\nSeines/winna leek wiſſus Keh-\nninus to Tautu no farweem\nKrehſleem zeltees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas wiſſi atbildehs un us\ntew fazzihſ: Ir tu effi wahſch\ntappis itt ka mehs/ tu effimums\nlihpf tappis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tawa Lepniba irr Ellē\nnogrimmuſi ar to Skannu ta-\nwo Rohflu/ Rohdas buhs taiwas\nZiffas/ un Tahrfi tewi apſegs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka effi tu no Debbes krit-\ntis tu Rihta-Swaigſne? tu\nDehls ta Auſekta ka effi tu pee\nSemmes nogabſts/ kas tu tohs\nLaudis pahrwarreji?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu fazziji taiwā Sir-\ndi: Es uſkahpfchu Debbesis/ es\npa-augſtinachu fawu Gohda-\nKrehſlu pahr tahm Deewa\nSwaigſnehm. Es apſehdeschohs\nus to * Sa-eefchanas Kalnu fah-\nnis Seemeſka-Puffi.\n* Tas Sa-eefchanas Kalns irr tas Kalns\nMorija, us ko tas Deewa Nams ſtahweja, un\neckſch ta tas Deewa Krehſlis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es uſkahpfchu pahr to\nPadebbeschu Augſtibahm/ es\ntapſchu tam Wiſſu-augſtajam\nſihds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teescham/ Ellē tapſi tu\nnorants fahnis teem Dſiltu-\nmeem,\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas tew redſehs/ tee ue-\nlubkoſs tewi un nemis tewi weh-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ra/ ( unt fazzichs:) Irrag ich\ntas Wihrs/ kas to Semmi k\nſtinaja un darrija Walſtibo\ndrebbam?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kasto Pafaull par Tub\nneſi darrija/ un winnas Piſſa-\ntus pohſtija/ kas taiwas Zeet\nma Laudis us Mahjahm ne a\nlaide.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi Kehnint to Pag\nnu/ tee wiſſi gull femmē\nGohdu/ ikweens taiwa Namim\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tu effi no taiwa Ka\npa atueſts ka neleetis Schagar\nka lahda Drehe to Nokant\nkas ar Sobbinu nodurti irr /\nka kas nokahpj lahda Akmi\nBedrē/ itt ka weena famiydi\nMaita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu ne tapſi klaht\nwinna aprakts/ jo tu effi tai\nSemmi maitajs/ un taiw\nLaudis nokawiſ/ to Launad\nritaju Dsimmums ne buhs i\nwehts muhſchigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Taiſajtees winna Bel\nnus kant winno Tehwo Apiv\nnoschanas deht/ ka tee ne zetta\nun eemanto to Semmi/ un p\npilda to Pafaull ar Piſſahtee\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo es zelfchohs prett tee\ntakka tas KUNGŚ Zebaot/\ntsdeldeschu no Babeles to Wa\ndu/ un tohs Atlikkuschus un\nDehlu/ un to Dehla Dehlu/\nka tas KUNGŚ:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es darrischu to\nIhvaſchuma teem Eſeem/ un\nUhdens Palteem/ un es ism\nſischu tohs ar to Slohtu t\nNon\n"
    }
  ],
